Run Docker

Docker command to run docker connection:
    docker run -p 3307:3306 --name mysqldb -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=root -e MYSQL_DATABASE=deliveryey mysql:8.0.13

Download MySQL WorkBench
Make a new connection
Set port to 3307
Test Connection

Edit run configuration command to:
    spring-boot:run -DMYSQL_USER=root -DMYSQL_PASSWORD=root -DMYSQL_PORT=3307

Configure application properties:
    spring:
      datasource:
        url: jdbc:mysql://${MYSQL_HOST:localhost}:${MYSQL_PORT:3306}/deliveryey
        username: ${MYSQL_USER:root}
        password:

Connect everything:
    docker run -p 8080:9090 --name deliveryey_mysql_docker --net spring-network -e MYSQL_HOST:mysqldb -e MYSQL_USER=root -e MYSQL_PASSWORD=root -e MYSQL_PORT=3306 deliveryey_mysql_docker
